Basic installation
------------------

  1. To compile the program type:

    make all

  2. You can remove the program binaries and object files by typing:

    make clean

Code documentation
------------------
 
To generate the code documentation the Doxygen must be installed. 
Just type:
  
  make documentation  

and the documentation will be generated and put in folders latex and html.
 
Requirements
------------

  1. ROOT (http://root.cern.ch) with properly paths

  2. gcc  

  3. Doxygen (www.doxygen.org) only if you want to generate 
     the code documentation

  4. BOOST packages:

Tested Platforms
----------------

  1. Ubuntu x86_64 GNU/Linux
    gcc 4.6.3
    ROOT v5.32
